Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:04.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Thank you, o great god Fukumoto! - by Me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:07.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji returns to the silver screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:13.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And we give you loyal anime watchers a sneak peek!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonight, for the final ep, we bring you a making-of!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:23.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Behind-the-scenes footage of Kaiji taking down the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I swallowed the Bog!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have to see the Bog go down in Kaiji 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And now, a quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:42.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Great God Fukumoto's Present Quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:46.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kiyomi is whose daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:48.81,kaiji-dialog,A,0,0,0,,A: Koji Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:51.79,kaiji-dialog,B,0,0,0,,B: Jun'ichi Ishida.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:54.62,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,C: Riko Higashio.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.93,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Well? Whose!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:01:01.05,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,The reward is a shikishi signed by the Great God Fukumoto himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.73,0:01:04.48,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Visit our mobile site to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.71,0:01:07.58,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,The anime may be over, but Kaiji is just getting started!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:19.01,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,0)\pos(640,505)}The Future is In Our Hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.22,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,It's paying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.52,0:01:21.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出る！出る！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,湯水のように！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.58,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,The balls are flowing like water!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.22,0:01:27.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸せー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:26.87,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:35.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確保の命令です　会長から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:33.88,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,We have direct orders from the Chairman to secure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お立ちください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.07,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:42.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ\Nうっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:39.58,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん ちょっと頼む\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:50.54,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Pops, keep an eye on this for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.06,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Uh, sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それはええが…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:55.85,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Ichijou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戻ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.67,0:01:59.41,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:06.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できる！お前ならできる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.04,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You can do it. I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:10.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこへ行こうと\N必ずその場を支配できる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.69,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,No matter where you end up, you'll claw your way to the top of the heap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策略 知略に長けた\N悪党だろ お前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:13.31,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You're a sly, scheming scumbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.37,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,So claw your way back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,這い上がってこい！\Nザコを蹴散らし 追い払い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:19.02,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Wipe out the small-time losers down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,這い上がってこい！\N倒してみろ 俺を！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.31,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,And come back up after me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:23.41,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Take me on again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… バカが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:26.24,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言われずとも そうするさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.68,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You don't even have to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.83,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.76,0:02:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ってろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:34.75,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,叩き潰す！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:39.89,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Next time, I will destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次は！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:52.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こうしてカイジ 対 一条\Nそのパチンコ勝負は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:51.43,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,And thus, the pachinko duel between Kaiji and Ichijou concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:58.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下カジノの主 ｢沼｣は\Nしぶとく執拗に抗い続けたが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:55.18,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,The Bog, the master of the underground casino,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.18,0:02:57.83,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,has put up a long and determined resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:02.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後に力尽き 放出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.49,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,But finally, its strength sapped, it paid out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:06.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのはらわたの全てを！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.50,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Paid out everything in its guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:08.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして換金！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:07.96,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,And then, the exchange!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見たことも\N想像したこともない大金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.20,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,A fortune the likes of which Kaiji had never seen nor even imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:15.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７億2910万！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:13.86,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,729,100,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まず 皆に祝儀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.19,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,First, they celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 返済
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.60,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Then, the repayment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:26.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何はともあれ帝愛の借金\N924万を返済する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:25.22,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Before anything else, Kaiji repays his debt of 9,240,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:29.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら 持ってけ 吸血野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.14,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,There! Take it, you bloodsuckers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:34.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソ野郎！あんな紙切れで\N人を奴隷扱いしやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.01,0:03:34.04,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You shitheads try to bleed men, drop by drop, until they become your slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:38.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざまあみろ　文句あるまい！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.84,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,This is what you get! How d'you like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:40.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は自由だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:39.98,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I'm free!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:44.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金ゼロ！金持ち！\N日本一の金持ち！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:41.63,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I don't owe a cent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.67,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm rich!  The richest man in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.91,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？\N俺も！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:50.21,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,And me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人 金持ち！億万長者！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.28,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,All three of us are rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.65,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Millionaires!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.08,0:04:02.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして分配！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.48,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Now, to split the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:06.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この時点で残金７億1786万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.25,0:04:05.96,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,At this moment, there's 717,860,000 yen left!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:10.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここからカイジが使った金を\N遠藤と坂崎に分配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:10.56,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,First, Endoh and Sakazaki take the same amount of money Kaiji's already spent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３人 同一条件とする
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.74,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,The three even up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:16.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして遠藤から借りた工作費
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:18.15,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Next, Endoh's construction budget, stack, and interest are paid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当日の軍資金と\N利子１億1326万が遠藤へ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:22.21,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Endoh takes 113,260,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:25.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに途中の追加軍資金が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:27.50,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Then, Kaiji's extra loans are paid back to Endoh and Sakazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:29.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤と坂崎にそれぞれ返され\N残ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.66,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,568,120,000 remain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:33.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５億6812万！これが純益
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.39,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,This is the net profit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:39.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを３等分\N１人頭 １億8937万！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:39.11,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Each of them gets 189,370,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:42.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤッホー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,割り切れない１万は\Nカイジがもらい 分配終了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.49,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Kaiji takes the remaining bill, and the money is split!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カンパーイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.17,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあさあ！こりゃ俺のおごりだ\Nおごり？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:51.86,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Look at it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.97,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,We're rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:55.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠慮は無用！\Nさあ飲もう！あとは飲もうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:55.02,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Let's drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしええのう 遠藤はんは\Nあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.72,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Man, you're lucky, Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって１人だけ夢の３億超え
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.71,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You're walking out of here with more than 300 mil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんまに羨ましい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.07,0:05:13.81,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I'm really jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… うん…\Nわしなんか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:23.85,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I put up 50 million to begin with, so I'm only really getting about 150 out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:20.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この勝負の前に5000万\Nいかれてもうてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:24.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実質の儲けは１億5000万ほどや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしが一番 実入りが少ないんや
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.92,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I kinda get the short end of the stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや ペケは俺さ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:29.56,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,No. That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:37.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話してなかったっけ\Nカ… カイジくん…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:35.26,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.11,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には救わなきゃならねえ仲間が\N５人いるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.99,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I have five friends I need to save.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:46.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地の底でともに\N艱難辛苦を超えてきた仲間が
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.64,0:05:45.75,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Friends I suffered with underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回 俺がシャバで\Nこんなバクチが打てたのも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:51.86,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,It's thanks to them that I even made it out here to gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの力なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの汗と涙と忍耐と
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:06:00.48,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Their sweat, their tears, their endurance... That's how I'm here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.30,0:06:00.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういうものの結晶として\N奇跡的に今 俺はここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:08.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ってわけだから その５人の救済
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:11.26,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,So I need to get them out and pay them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,借金返済だけは しなきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その費用が約5000万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.91,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,It's gonna be about 50 mil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:19.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さらに残った１億4000万も\Nその５人と俺で割る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:19.11,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,And I'm splitting the 140 left with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:21.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\N割る？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.34,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You're splitting it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:26.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連中は 言うなら俺の外ウマに\N乗ったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.69,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,They bet on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 利益は６人で\N割らなきゃいけない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:28.60,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,So I need to split what I won with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:32.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とすると １人頭およそ2300万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:32.90,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,That leaves each of us with 23 million or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:36.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ちょ… ちょっと待てよ\Nカイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:38.52,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Wait, Kaiji! You don't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまですることは なかろう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下の仲間か何か知らんが\N６等分は やりすぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.35,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I don't know how close you guys got down there, but a six-way split is overkill!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.81,0:06:45.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地下から救い出せば それで十分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:45.59,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Just getting them out is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上の報酬は せんでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:48.51,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,They don't need any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあまあ　あの金をどう使おうと\Nカイジの勝手だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:52.76,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Eh, it's up to Kaiji how he spends his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:56.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そりゃそうやが…\N認めるしかねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.85,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I guess....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.35,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Just deal with it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに立派ってこった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.64,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,It's pretty badass, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:03.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今時 珍しい友情厚き男ってわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.35,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Here's a man who really knows the value of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせよ\Nうーん 分からん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.50,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Aww, c'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.94,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:10.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からん！何でそうなるんか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:10.08,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Why do you have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから外ウマってのはな\Nそういうもんなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:13.81,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I told you, they bet on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ！さっきの一条の件といい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:15.73,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:19.42,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He proved just how naïve he is with Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.51,0:07:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直ってねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.47,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He's never gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつの妙な善人ぶり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.95,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He's never gonna get over trying to be the nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい加減にせえよ\Nしょうがねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束しちまったもんは！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:35.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すくわれて当然だな\Nこんなんじゃ足を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:34.69,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He's still an easy mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,進歩ゼロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:37.27,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He hasn't learned a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いずれ食い殺される\Nそんな考えじゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.23,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Sooner or later, someone'll hang him out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:44.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救えねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:42.92,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,He's never gonna change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:50.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ人や！わしが間違っとった！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.51,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You're such a great guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.80,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I was wrong about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:52.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジくん\Nえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:53.77,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Kaiji! You can have my... My...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしの大事な…\N金？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:54.76,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:59.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金より大事な…\Nはあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.01,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Something more important than money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,美心を！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:00.93,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Mikoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？\N持ってけ 泥棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:06.21,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Take her, you bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え… 遠慮しときます
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:07.76,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カーッ 何て慎み深い！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.20,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You don't have to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや 慎みじゃなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.88,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Believe me, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気に入った！\Nますます気に入った！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:16.80,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You've fallen for her! I know you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.60,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Pops?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:30.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーあ　へっ 大して\N飲んでねえのに だらしがねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.41,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,What a lightweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 遠藤さ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:33.48,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Right, En... doh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:40.09,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:43.79,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Whaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:50.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無味無臭の睡眠薬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:49.17,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Tasteless, scentless sleeping pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水に入れても気づかない代物だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.74,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You wouldn't even notice them in water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ ４～５時間 眠っててくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:56.04,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a little nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして４時間後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:04.40,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Four hours pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… なっ 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.01,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝ちまったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.75,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Did I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:19.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？いない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.27,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Huh, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ？遠藤さん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:22.02,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Hey? Endoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:26.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっちゃん　おっちゃん 起きろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:26.02,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Pops! Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:33.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消えたぞ　遠藤さんが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.17,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Endoh's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,トイレやないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:34.91,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:37.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かめたが いない\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:36.19,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,I just checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？ああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァー 大丈夫や
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:50.86,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He probably just went to pay his loans off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:51.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多分 借金返しに行ったんやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… なっ ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:53.87,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.57,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,No, it's not all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ていうか 少ない！俺の金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:10:00.43,kaiji-dialog,C,0,0,0,,My money! It's gone, gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nない　ない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.66,kaiji-ed,{ts,0,0,0,,To Kaiji
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:15.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,喜びの宴に水を差すのも\N何だと思い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:17.83,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,Sorry to rain on your parade, but I had to take the money and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな形で切り出すしかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.63,0:10:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は最後に俺が\Nトイレで貸し付けた1000万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:22.76,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,The ten million you borrowed from me in the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:27.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金利をもらっていなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.64,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,I forgot to charge you the interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:32.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同封してあるあの時の借用書を\Nよーく見てほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:31.82,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,Take a close look at the contract you signed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお！\Nうわ！ひどっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:41.08,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明記してあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:42.94,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,It should be as clear as day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:47.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢10分３割複利｣と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:45.78,kaiji-dialog,{ts,0,0,0,,Compound interest, 30% per ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が あの1000万を渡したのが\N午後12時15分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:50.83,kaiji-dialog,I lent you that 10 million at 12,0,0,0,,I lent you that 10 million at 12:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:54.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大当たりが決まり\N返済可能となったのが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:56.50,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,You hit the jackpot and could pay it back at 1:47.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,午後１時47分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その間 92分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.83,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,That's 92 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:04.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 1000万を３割複利で\N10回 回した計算になり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:04.31,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,So the 30% interest compounded ten times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その金利は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:10.00,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,That makes the interest 127,850,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億2785万になる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,う… ぐうっ…\Nカイジくん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは お前に個人的に\N貸し付けた借金だから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:21.60,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,You borrowed it yourself, so I took it out of your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の取り分から\N受け取っていくぞ　悪く思うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.59,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Fair's fair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:29.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは俺の当然の権利なのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:27.02,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I had the right to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:35.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけ… ふざけんなよ 遠藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:33.80,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Give me a fucking break, Endoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.77,0:11:40.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけ… ふざけやがって　遠藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:40.73,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,You cocksucker! Endoh, you cocksucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局 １億8938万から
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:51.18,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,127,850,000 yen is taken from Kaiji's 189,380,000, reducing him to 61,530,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:47.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１億2785万を取られ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残ったのは6153万！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:55.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 名残惜しいが\N俺はこれで失礼する
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:55.31,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's a shame we have to part, but I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.89,0:11:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体に気をつけて暮らせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:12:00.50,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Take care, Kaiji, my dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:01.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親愛なるカイジへ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:09.38,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Why me!? Why does this always happen to {\i1}me{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何でこんな目に…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が… 俺だけが…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:13.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カ… カイジくん…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.68,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Kaiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:18.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ！そうそう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:16.82,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:21.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしも そろそろ行かんと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.94,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I need to get going.
