Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:36.41,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,You're all such awesome guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさんは？\Nカイジさんはどこだよ？
