Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:40.12,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Where's Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　散れ！散れ 散れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:44.22,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Scram, you hear?
