Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.67,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,What about Kaiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.01,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:51.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでたまってる　散れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.42,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna stand there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.45,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Clear out! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 散れ 散れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分からん男だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.84,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした？\Nどうして会いに行かない？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:06.73,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.98,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Why didn't you go see them? They were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:13.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな会いたがってたぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:16.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも …ねがないから\Nは？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.03,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,But I'm flat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:20.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あの 金がないから…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.11,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I'm broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:22.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,え？バカな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:20.86,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.88,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Really? Penniless?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえってこと ねえだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田の救出金が\N1000万ちょいだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.52,0:19:32.13,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Even after Ishida, there should have been about 600 thou left. A hundred each.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:32.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,60万ほど残って\Nその６分の１の10万
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日 お前に渡しただろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:37.07,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I gave it to you myself yesterday. Where'd it all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:38.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでねえんだよ その金が？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.89,0:19:42.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パチンコで…\Nはっ？パチンコ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.11,0:19:40.07,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Pachinko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:42.31,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Pachinko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:46.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか すっちまったのか 10万？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:48.13,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,You blew a hundred thou on pachinko in a single day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.63,0:19:48.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日で おい？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ！残しとけよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:53.02,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot? You knew you were meeting them today, you should've saved some!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるだろ 今日会うことは
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:56.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱くなって 気がついたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:56.21,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I got caught up in the game and lost track...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:59.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞きたかねえ そんなクズの常套句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:59.08,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Wow, you really are trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まーったく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:05.39,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,Jeez, why can't you go meet them even if you're broke?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.94,0:20:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに 金がなくったって\N会うことぐらい できるだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:10.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな！会ったら絶対\N飲み食いになるじゃないっすか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:09.71,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I can't! I know they'd want to go out for dinner and drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:14.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そん時 金がないから\Nおごってくれなんて とても…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.91,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I can't just sponge off of them...
