Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:29.40,kaiji-dialog,You hit the jackpot and could pay me back at 1,0,0,0,,I don't even know if you're too humble or too proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:31.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チェッ
